room_title: Escape room "Fair Game" by Red Door Escape Room Concord in Concord
room_description: The magicians need your help! You and your team stumbled into a magic carnival and are on a quest to find a peculiar set of playing cards. Your have one hour to find the missing cards before the show starts! And if that wasn't enough pressure, you can play this episode with up to 12 people in a 6 v 6, head-to-head competition. Full of hands-on puzzles, Fair Game is recommended for family and friend groups who love outside the box thinking.
